Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好像...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被綁架過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.24,0:00:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紅眼睛的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我認識
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是現在發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我進入某個人的意識中了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.83,0:01:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對 不應該
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這怎麼會是Hikari的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,木神並沒這麼說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:54.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想看看你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 看關關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,背著光 就看到裡面的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,片名：夜來（4）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們知道透過宮阪的言靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把SHINYA召到地上的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我得追上大家才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個區域已經沒有敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知不覺跟大家走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家應該沒有事得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們得目的地相同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很快就可以會合得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過若是中途支撐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可別成為別人的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這麼說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我從剛剛開始 不也幫了不少忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜歡性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪裡舒服呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有很多好戲那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你盡量享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣我就能變回人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一個換我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在所有HIKARI從黑暗世界 移動出來還需要一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們君臨這個世界 的時刻終於來臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在等待這值得慶賀 的時刻的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想去切斷後顧之憂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這麼在意葉村的妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對現在的你來說 應該不足為俱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要在這裡等她上來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這個天生的HIKAR 是不會瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這與那是不同的兩碼子事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.59,0:06:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要跟你做個了結 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在沙漠的寂靜 造訪這個世界之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.01,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉 我吵醒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是夢 你真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前我也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我戰鬥的理由是為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從今以後 我會一直陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要拿出壓箱寶物了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你退下 大姐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼 大家呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等你醒來我們就追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們還要我們代為傳話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你別太賣命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫我要更努力...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是從哪裡弄來炸藥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的朋友中有 喜歡玩這種危險東西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過太不堪一擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說是HIKARI 連玻璃都炸的沒有蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你差點連我們都炸死耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使用火藥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來你們出動時 還是有做一些準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼搞的 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又得用那一招了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.28,0:09:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,部長 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,京華他們好像在門的對面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿星 你不會幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姚瀨跟阿誠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟大家走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 要開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你來了 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來解決上次的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好趕在一切都結束之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前我要你先說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐被你帶去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道這個有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美裡在我給她的睡眠中 得到永遠的安詳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種騙人的安詳...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:09:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小白！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.93,0:10:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被抹去記憶而活的人 嘗到的煉獄是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的你是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.08,0:10:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發現過去搶走自己的情人 的妹妹在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,美裡會做何感受？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉 我不只是為了向 火蛇之裡的老人報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而選擇這條路的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是在尋找中發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真正的安息只存在毀滅中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉 光靠人世間的道理 是無法拯救靈魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要毀滅 大哥你自己毀滅就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:53.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為美裡與哥哥們 不敢正視兩人重要的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥 你的作法是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來我們還是到了 不得不動手的地步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原諒我 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥 覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.88,0:11:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丈！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只說一次 不准妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丈 退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:12:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說過不准妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是我們繼承 火蛇血統的人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,切斷惡因果之鎖 是我在火蛇之裡的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼教導我 提拔我這沒能力的人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（咒）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別吵 這點傷不算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你別動 阿誠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我馬上幫你止血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,丈 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像受傷不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還想打的話 我們奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:13:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很想陪你們打
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惜沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小白！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面臨最後的審判
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的內心卻有迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不知道你們是不是 能阻止HIKARI的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我已經讓使魔 記住美裡沉眠的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來讓美裡的靈魂醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:08.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,HIKARI是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能是人心的弱點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.54,0:14:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們體內也有HIKARI吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是別的夢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.83,0:15:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰睡在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了 別吵我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎光臨 各位火蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得你們能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.26,0:15:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晃一 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡 原來你是HIKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.79,0:15:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了難得一訪的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我幫你們把同伴找來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人類絕望的表情 每次看都好可愛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們別妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為你們已經被 我的使僕們包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小麗的樣子怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你對小麗做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 看不到總司的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是被你們打敗了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.71,0:16:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直掛念著無聊的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抹殺掉美裡這女人 記憶的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！你是她妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候為了讓總司 投向HIKARI這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.00,0:16:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛好他為了你的事 內心產生動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於是就被我們說動了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真該謝謝你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的知識對我們幫助很大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總司對美裡那個女人 下的沉眠法術
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也對這孩子下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被施法術的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將害怕醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會抱住給予的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠躺在黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像是這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種小法術算什...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我 丈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我勸你別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.91,0:17:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在勉強搖醒她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的靈魂會被黑暗撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時後果可不堪設想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來在深夜之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得請你們 暫時在那裡乖一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 來說點故事打發無聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在平安時代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,HIKARI得到來往這世界 的媒介時的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身為媒介而出聲的女人 名字叫竹取公主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,擁有神奇能力的她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以那能力和美貌 吸引了當權者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是由於拒絕入宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而被當成混亂世間的災難 被處火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無辜死去的她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那強烈的恨意在這個世間 打開了與黑暗世界的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鏈接異世界的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被稱為新月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的遺腹子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是擁有 紅與藍色眼珠的雙胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是你們火蛇的祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火蛇害怕我們從黑暗世界移動過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功封印了新月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後在封印旁邊 建立了火蛇之裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代代守護下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 總司的背叛 使得封印被解開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新月復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:56.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最初的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本來是想 讓火蛇的親兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總司與小泉成為 HIKARI大進攻的促進劑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我與哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竹取公主的子孫 手足相殘的修羅景象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是將世界推進黑暗 的最棒的促進劑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果沒有你們妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這時候應該...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來你就是這樣 專門鑽人的心理弱點的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩 要動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轟轟烈烈的幹一番
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看大家的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣條件就平等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 你們這些小人物 沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（咒）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噫...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能讓我開心一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉 能不能借力量給我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起來啦 小麗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 起床也沒什麼好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要一直在這裡睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你再這麼說 看我不搔你的癢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 住手 別啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡是哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.46,0:22:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直走 結果就來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之回家吧 先回大家身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不破壞這個集光系統的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能還會出現第二、第三個 想引來HIKARI大進攻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葉村 你能動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起來吧 小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身體已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種夢...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種感覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 宮阪也沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.71,0:24:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼 你的傷會不會痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對哦 你的力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.47,0:24:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以的 阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.01,0:25:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.18,0:26:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.75,0:27:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿涼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.27,0:27:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小泉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.91,0:28:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,換下一個了 大家走
